                            <comment id="13005163" author="jbellis" created="Thu, 10 Mar 2011 17:07:49 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;fix bytesPastMark to return long.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Note that if your row index is &amp;gt; 2GB then you should probably increase column_index_size_in_kb to 256 or higher.  I&apos;ve created &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-2308&quot; title=&quot;add tracing of cell name index effectiveness&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;CASSANDRA-2308&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;CASSANDRA-2308&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; to expose row index size so this can be tuned more accurately.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13005761" author="slebresne" created="Fri, 11 Mar 2011 18:16:48 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;It breaks BufferedRandomAccessFileTest.&lt;br/&gt;
But +1 on the patch otherwise.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
